<Page x:Class="Hardcodet.Wpf.Samples.Help.PutCaretPosition"
	xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
	xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
	Title="PutCaretPosition" 
	>
    <FlowDocumentReader ViewingMode="Scroll">
        <FlowDocument FontSize="20">
            <Paragraph>
                <Image Source="/Images/help1.png" Width="190" Height="190" Margin="0,0,30,0" />
                <Run FontSize="30" BaselineAlignment="Center">PutCaretPositionInArray</Run>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold FontSize="24">Examples:</Bold>
            </Paragraph>
            <List>
                <ListItem>
                    <Paragraph>
                        <Bold>PutCaretPositionInArray</Bold>
                    </Paragraph>
                    <Table CellSpacing="5" BorderThickness="1" BorderBrush="Black">
                        <TableRowGroup>
                            <TableRow>
                                <TableCell>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Image Source="/Images/PrimitivesPutCaretPosition.PNG"  Margin="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalAlignment="Center" />
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </TableCell>
                            </TableRow>
                        </TableRowGroup>
                    </Table>
                    <Table CellSpacing="5" BorderThickness="1" BorderBrush="Black">
                        <TableRowGroup>
                            <TableRow>
                                <TableCell>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Image Source="/Images/ArraysPutCaretPosition.PNG"  Margin="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalAlignment="Center" />
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </TableCell>
                            </TableRow>
                        </TableRowGroup>
                    </Table>                    
                    <Table CellSpacing="5" BorderThickness="1" BorderBrush="Black">
                        <TableRowGroup>
                            <TableRow>
                                <TableCell>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        <Image Source="/Images/LogicPutCaretPosition.PNG"  Margin="5,5,5,5"  HorizontalAlignment="Center" />
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </TableCell>
                            </TableRow>
                        </TableRowGroup>
                    </Table>

                    <Paragraph>
                        <Italic>Explanation of example</Italic> - 1. Minimize IdealAutomate. 2. Launch notepad. 3. Wait 3 seconds. 4. PutCaretPositionInArray. 5. Type text Hello World. 6. Wait 3 seconds. 7. Click where caret originally was.
                        <LineBreak/>
                    </Paragraph>
                </ListItem>


            </List>
            <Paragraph>
                <Line Stretch="Fill" Stroke="Black" X2="1"/>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold FontSize="24">Columns:</Bold>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                <Bold>PutCaretPositionInArray</Bold> - PutCaretPositionInArray provides a way to save the caret position in an array so you can come back to it later without having to find the original position again. Here are the columns:
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        1. Sequence
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Sequence is a decimal number with 4 digits after the decimal. It can be modified to allow you to insert rows anywhere in your script. Rows are executed in sequence number order.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        2. Verb
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                PutCaretPositionInArray
            </Paragraph>


            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        3. Entity1
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Entity1 is the name of a array that has been defined in the Arrays tab. PutCaretPosition puts the X and Y coordinates of the cursor into the array.
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        4. Relationship
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Relationship is not used
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        5. Entity2
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Entity2 is not used.
            </Paragraph>





        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentReader>
</Page>
